v0.7.0 - xx/10/04
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * New 'RainDrop image' plugin using Pieter Voloshyn algorithm. 
    * New Emboss algorithm from Pieter Voloshyn. 
    * New OilPaint algorithm from Pieter Voloshyn. 
    * Add graphical banner with logo.
    * Fixed Digikam headers depencies.

v0.6.0 - 09/01/04
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Fixed internationalization problem (bad localization files name).
    * Using QSlider/QSpinbox instead KIntNumInput and KDoubleNumInput for 
      Despeckle, Unsharped mask, Charcoal, OilPaint, and Emboss plugins : 
      solving a problem with the preview calculation when the sliders are moved.
    
v0.5.0 - 08/27/04
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Added new unsharped mask filter plugin using Gimp 2.0 algorithm.
    * Updated noise reduction filter plugin with Gimp 2.0 algorithm.

v0.4.0 - 08/26/04
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Added new Charcoal drawing effect plugin using KDEImageEffect API.
    * Added new Emboss effect plugin using KDEImageEffect API.
    * Added new Oil painting effect plugin using KDEImageEffect API.
    
v0.3.0 - 08/25/04
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Added new noise reduction filter 'Despeckle' plugin using KDEImageEffect API.

v0.2.0 - 08/15/04
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Moved 'SolarizeImage' plugin from Digikam core.

v0.1.0 - 08/11/04
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Initial Creation : 'AdjustLevels' plugin.
